                    <p>We began by conducting joint strategy sessions with the client’s physicians, administrators, and IT staff to map real-world challenges to digital workflows. The goal was to design an EHR system that was intuitive, cloud-based, and fully compliant, enabling healthcare providers to manage records efficiently, even offline when connectivity is limited.</p>

                    <h3 id="keyHighlight">Key Features Implemented:</h3>
