                        <li><strong>Offline Access:</strong> Enabled critical data access during network downtime, ensuring uninterrupted service.</li>
                        <li><strong>Customizable Reports & Analytics:</strong> Physicians could generate specialized reports, track patient progress, and gain insights through Power BI integration.</li>
                        <li><strong>Document Scanning & Workflow Automation:</strong> Built-in document management allowed easy upload, categorization, and sharing of records with internal and external teams.</li>
                        <li><strong>Secure Data Sharing:</strong> Implemented controlled access protocols and end-to-end encryption for sharing data across departments and facilities.</li>
                        <li><strong>Child Growth Tracking:</strong> Developed visual growth charts that alert doctors to potential health concerns early.</li>
